{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ImageData()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageData/ImageData","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><em><code>ImageData()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageData/data\"><code>data</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageData/height\"><code>height</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageData/width\"><code>width</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Canvas API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasPattern\"><code>CanvasPattern</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmapRenderingContext\"><code>ImageBitmapRenderingContext</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas\"><code>OffscreenCanvas</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/createImageBitmap\"><code>createImageBitmap</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>ImageData()</strong></code> 构造函数返回一个新的实例化的&nbsp;<code style=\"font-style: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">ImageData</code>&nbsp;对象，&nbsp; 此对象由给定的类型化数组和指定的宽度与高度组成。</p>\n\n<p>这个构造器是创建像这种对象首选的方式。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">new ImageData(<em>array</em>, <em>width</em>, <em>height</em>);\n<em>n</em>ew ImageData(<em>width</em>, <em>height</em>);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"array\"><code>array </code></dt>\n <dd>包含图像隐藏像素的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Uint8ClampedArray\"><code>Uint8ClampedArray</code></a> 数组。如果数组没有给定，指定大小的黑色矩形图像将会被创建。</dd>\n <dt id=\"width\"><code>width</code></dt>\n <dd>无符号长整型（unsigned long）数值，描述图像的宽度。</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect1\">&nbsp;<code>height</code></dt>\n <dd>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 无符号长整型（unsigned long）数值，描述图像的高度。</dd>\n <dd>如果已给定数组，这个值是可选的：它将通过它的大小和给定的宽度进行推断。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js  language-js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> imageData <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ImageData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Creates a 100x100 black rectangle</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ImageData { width: 100, height: 100, data: Uint8ClampedArray[40000] }</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"specification","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/canvas.html#dom-imagedata-dev","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.ImageData.ImageData"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.ImageData.ImageData","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageData/ImageData/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createImageData\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.createImageData()</code></a>, the creator method that can be used outside workers.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"specification"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"ImageData() 构造函数返回一个新的实例化的 ImageData 对象，  此对象由给定的类型化数组和指定的宽度与高度组成。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"ImageData()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/imagedata/imagedata","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/imagedata/imagedata/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageData","title":"ImageData"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageData/ImageData","title":"ImageData()"}],"pageTitle":"ImageData() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}